    @SPI
public class ProjectionEventDelivery<I,P extends Projection<I,?,?>>
extends Delivery<I,P,io.spine.core.EventEnvelope,EventShardedStream<I>,EventShardedStream.Builder<I>>
    A strategy on delivering the events to the instances of a certain projection type.

    Spine users may want to extend this class in order to switch to another delivery mechanism.
